{"tid":1394912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉華表態! 劉德華決定取消今年生日會!","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:51:59.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1454,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"29d142d80e32da7dd51c85d565cf57c094e1fb82","tid":1394912,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"劉德華向來視他的歌迷為家人，每年都會提早舉行生日會，與一眾「家人」齊齊慶祝。以往劉華攜帶朱麗倩及女兒出席，可見劉華對歌迷會的「家人」多重視。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今年劉華就決定取消生日會，但沒有透露因，歌迷會亦已安排退款事宜。不少人得悉消息之後，大感失望，但仍支持劉華的決定。"},{"pid":"64e169058b6b1b2117fd1853df9fe6a10288d231","tid":1394912,"uid":149494,"like":12,"dislike":428,"score":-416,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"多謝華仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3653bd818eae4d5bd71beac7a031d41b312aeabd","tid":1394912,"uid":125029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"同我瘋狂推爆「公務員事務局」FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa006ac6b847480c6994d36248d45b9c6883dde8","tid":1394912,"uid":39205,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"【 香港可能面對緊一場極大嘅人道災難 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c6705e66c49332449f05bfbf7b6e1f325082e99","tid":1394912,"uid":43141,"like":744,"dislike":4,"score":740,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"嘩! 取消生日會呀! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3142e9e7c9a4619bbf992